# append(contentsOf:)

**Instance Method**

Appends the contents of a column slice to the column.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(contentsOf other: AnyColumnSlice)
```

## Parameters

- **other**: A column that contains elements of the same type as this column.

## Adding Elements

- **append(_:)**: Appends an optional element to the column.
- **append(contentsOf:)**: Appends the contents of another column to the column.
